  "detailed_description": "A survival strategy indie-game. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/72c7313367f43aa699ba26a9ccd9f440.poster.avif?t=1742201620\" width=650 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/72c7313367f43aa699ba26a9ccd9f440.webm?t=1742201620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/72c7313367f43aa699ba26a9ccd9f440.mp4?t=1742201620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gather resources, expand your village, explore the underground for riches and train soldiers...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/f49638342fb4d99b72bc50b0b09c1cd7.poster.avif?t=1742201620\" width=650 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/f49638342fb4d99b72bc50b0b09c1cd7.webm?t=1742201620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/f49638342fb4d99b72bc50b0b09c1cd7.mp4?t=1742201620\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>... to defend against hordes of the undead!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/358ce35e650a5123e3a9d0d44f88caf9.poster.avif?t=1742201620\" width=650 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/358ce35e650a5123e3a9d0d44f88caf9.webm?t=1742201620\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/947300/extras/358ce35e650a5